        <mxCell id="flow-note" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f0f0f0;strokeColor=#999999;fontSize=11;align=left;spacingLeft=8;" value="&lt;b&gt;Request Flow&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;1. Client sends GET /pokemons&lt;br&gt;2. Controller parses query &amp;amp; sort params&lt;br&gt;3. Service checks PokemonCache&lt;br&gt;   &lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;a. Cache HIT → use cached list&lt;br&gt;   &lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;b. Cache MISS → call PokeApiClient&lt;br&gt;&lt;blockquote style=&quot;margin: 0 0 0 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;      → fetch from PokéAPI (HTTP)&lt;br&gt;      → store in cache (TTL 1h)&lt;/blockquote&gt;4. Filter list by query substring&lt;br&gt;5. Sort filtered list via Strategy&lt;br&gt;6. Return JSON response" vertex="1">
